data.description: Cute and spacious ranch with attached garage!  One level living with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and main level laundry. Home features an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, hardwood flooring and large fenced in yard. Living room opens to kitchen and dining room area. New carpet throughout main level. Master suite has large bathroom with double vanity and walk in closet.  Huge finished basement set up to be a rec room or family room.  Lower level has a 4th non-conforming bedroom along with a half bath. Excellent location within minutes from Legends shopping and dining, Sporting KC, Kansas Speedway and Dub’s Dread Golf Course!
